<h2 id="readme">README</h2>

<p>We built a space photo of the day page using the astronomy picture of the day API provided by NASA. This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Space photo or video, updated daily</li>
  <li>Title and description of the photo/video</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="data">Data</h2>

<p>Data used for this project:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://data.cdc.gov/NNDSS/NNDSS-Weekly-Data/x9gk-5huc">National Notifiable Diseases Surveillance System API</a> (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention)</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="kudos">Kudos</h2>

<p>Big kudos to CDC for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Maintaining a developer portal and public API.</li>
</ul>

